Octociz is still looking for the Ark when he hears sgots being fired 
up ahead. He goes over to see that he has finaly reached the 
Maximals. He looks over and sees many of them fighting one giant bot. 
It is giving of a strange energy signal. Not Pred and not Maximal. 

"This must be the alliance they told us about," thought 
Octociz, "Well I won't stand for it. I won't see Maximals hurt. That 
one dinosaur bot over there is probably going to sacrifice it's self. 
Well, it's time for me to show my Maximal colors!"

Octociz transforms to Beast Mode. He pulls out his 2 blasters and 
gets his ink shooters ready. He made need them to rust up his parts. 
Octociz runs and starts opening fire on the large bot.
